{"type":null,"faqId":37086,"title":"手环如何检测我的运动和睡眠状态？为什么我的B2手环睡眠统计数据不准？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>手环内部安装了业界领先的六轴加速度传感器，精密的仪器搭配尖端的技术，轻松识别您的睡眠、运动状态（走路、跑步、骑行）。手环传感器通过识别用户的动作幅度/频率/动作的前后逻辑来判断用户的状态，以识别是睡眠还是运动。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>睡眠统计的原理是通过传感器对于睡眠状态下手腕的动作来判断睡眠状态。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>--如果是睡眠数据丢失。可能是用户睡眠时手腕动作较多，使传感器判断为非睡眠，导致数据丢失。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>--如果是睡眠数据误增。可能是手环处于相对比较安静的状态下，并且出现了与睡眠相似的这种动作幅度，使传感器判断为睡眠状态，导致数据误增。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2250","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750142000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":143,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":6,"times":2,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,睡眠 运动 统计 睡眠数据 运动数据","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}